    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 25,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Sangonomiya Kokomi_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "珊瑚宮心海",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器的副詞綴雖然對心海作用較小，但武器特效在操作合宜的情況下可以保證更久持續元素戰技，從另一方面保證了隊伍整體的持續治療量與持續掛水能力。缺點是比較依賴高精煉度，是心海可用的武器之一。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 30,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Sucrose_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "砂糖",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "在隊伍配置中，砂糖一般是作為一名輔助",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "方面的角色，該武器的副詞綴可以提高砂糖的輔助能力。砂糖元素戰技產出能量較多但冷卻時間較長，配合該武器技能可以有效提高隊伍風系角色的充能效率，如果解鎖了第一命之座，甚至可以做到元素戰技三連發，是比較適合輔助型砂糖的武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
